data.description: Charming manufactured home in the desirable Lincoln Terrace Community of just 43 homes. Enter the 3-bedroom 2 bath home to discover the welcoming living room with neutral palette, vaulted ceilings, abundant natural light and new carpet throughout. The large living room is accented by the dual sided fireplace and lovely built-in cabinets.  The fully equipped open kitchen has an abundance of cabinets, gas stove, large island, and tile counters. The large primary bedroom features dual closets and a private en-suite bath w/dual sinks. A true split floor plan with the guest rooms and second bath at the opposite end of the home. This property also has a large carport and screened Patio that looks to the Rincon Mountains. You don't want to miss this value.
